published the first paper

00:04:06.570 --> 00:04:08.790
describing that
supernova and went on

00:04:08.790 --> 00:04:11.750
to study this Rosetta Stone
for astronomers of wavelengths,

00:04:11.750 --> 00:04:13.830
from the infrared to gamma rays.

00:04:13.830 --> 00:04:16.190
